casebody.data:
Randolph G. WILSON, Jr.
v.
Teresa L. WILSON 2150259 Court of Civil Appeals of Alabama. March 2, 2018 Terrie Scott Morgan of Capell & Howard, P.C., Montgomery, for petitioner. John Olszewski of Minor & Olszewski, L.L.C., Montgomery, for respondent. After Remand from the Supreme Court of Alabama THOMPSON, Presiding Judge.

The prior judgment of this court has been reversed and the cause remanded by the Supreme Court of Alabama. Ex parte Wilson , 262 So.3d 1202 (Ala. 2018). On remand to this court, and in compliance with the supreme court's opinion, the judgment of the trial court is hereby reversed and remanded.

REVERSED AND REMANDED.

Pittman, Thomas, Moore, and Donaldson, JJ., concur.
